<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Harris KX: 50 тестів (модуляції, режими, модеми, вокодери)</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f0f4fa;
            color: #1a2639;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #0b2a4a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #3a6ea5;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .stats-panel {
            background: #f8fafd;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border: 1px solid #d0ddeb;
        }
        .score-box {
            background: #1e3a5f;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .btn-group button {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #1e3a5f;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-group button:hover {
            background: #1e3a5f;
            color: white;
        }
        .question-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .question-card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #d4e0f0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .question-card.correct {
            background: #e1f7e8;
            border-left: 5px solid #2e7d32;
        }
        .question-card.incorrect {
            background: #ffefed;
            border-left: 5px solid #ba1a1a;
        }
        .q-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .q-num {
            background: #d4e0f0;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .option {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background: #f5f9ff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .option:hover {
            background: #dde7f5;
        }
        .option input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 15px;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
        }
        .feedback {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background: #f9fbfe;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 3px solid #7895b8;
        }
        .correct-msg { color: #2e7d32; font-weight: bold; }
        .wrong-msg { color: #ba1a1a; font-weight: bold; }
        .explain { margin-top: 8px; color: #2c3e50; }
        hr { margin: 25px 0; border: 1px solid #d0ddeb; }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>📡 Harris KX • 50 тестів</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">модуляції, режими роботи, модеми, вокодери (за конспектом)</div>

    <div class="stats-panel">
        <span class="score-box" id="scoreDisplay">0/50</span>
        <div class="btn-group">
            <button id="checkAllBtn">✅ Перевірити всі</button>
            <button id="resetBtn">🔄 Скинути</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="questionsContainer" class="question-grid"></div>
    
    <hr>
    <footer>Для молодшої сестри • На основі конспекту Harris KX</footer>
</div>

